{"tid":394738,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港男大鬧墾丁大街搗亂商店 遭途人痛毆倒地","createTime":"2017-09-10T08:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T10:23:30.000Z","uid":119979,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d54c9a2a16c516700391242f10ea8fe48268fbe","tid":394738,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:18:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170910/57191685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170910%2F57191685&d=K3dCVXl4wAKZNk47p1F0uLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=157af9d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170910%2F57191685&h=b73df5f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170910/57191685</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚影衰 屌你老母"},{"pid":"be76db0c6260d8e169ebc3fa14fbaf584eb67b33","tid":394738,"uid":119979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:19:12.000Z","msg":"又是酒後亂性？一名39歲、名叫吳浩賢的香港男子，昨晚深夜與友人在墾丁大街酒醉後，沿路不斷亂踢垃圾桶及攤位，還到一間服飾店內搗亂，有路見不平的遊客見狀，馬上上前將吳痛毆，令他倒地不起。事後警方接報到場，將吳鎖上手銬，送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n事發昨晚11時許，酒醉的吳浩然與鄭姓等7名友人在墾丁大街上逛街，<span style=\"color: red;\">吳沿路騷擾攤位及腳踢垃圾桶，甚至對着遊客大聲以英文及粵語怒罵叫囂，在墾丁大街南端被一群看不過眼的遊客痛毆，吳被打趴倒地不起，鄭姓友人急忙道歉打圓場。</span><br />\n吳起身後，走到大街北端一家服飾店搗亂破壞衣褲，警方據報到場後，吳男酒醒大半，先賠償服飾店損失，被鎖上手銬後送至南門醫院。由於全案沒有任何人員提告，警方登記資料勸戒後，便將吳男送交其友人照顧。<br />\n<br />\n恆春警分局長曾學貴指出，搗亂事件發生後，警方便派出快打部隊到場，迅速將混亂場面控制，整個過程不到30分鐘，呼籲民眾面對類似情況立刻報警並遠離失控者，避免攻擊或接近對方，以免發生危險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班朋友見佢比人打先至出聲 唔一早阻止佢周圍搞亂 痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf6afda1136724fa83fc8053cce0dfb67b953f5","tid":394738,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58c505d327b8298d12b2f1ca4abc77230e4d3541","tid":394738,"uid":28624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:33:39.000Z","msg":"好心飲完酒會發酒癲既人咪撚飲啦<br />\n正垃圾害人害物冇鬼用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed524b2cabf933ebe5555474951af66e648bae6","tid":394738,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fbc19a7ac6226132ebff002175f0e96bfcf1705","tid":394738,"uid":3571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9dc9ffd28cc5668f74f04cd2c081e212e5e9ab4","tid":394738,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d29559f4a37a251a90edcc12bf326695e01186","tid":394738,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"夠哂朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fd12513c94bd04ab8f0eb14596786a50946877","tid":394738,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:08:46.000Z","msg":"渣 ga  中左人地幾拳就扮死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036e1d3abdee7965adf36ce3b5fb64398a2e2657","tid":394738,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:23:30.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}